### Summary of the Paper
IAL proposes a Player-Advisor self-play loop to autonomously generate preference data for LLM alignment, and SPACP, a hinge-penalty variant of DPO to prevent Bradley-Terry degeneration. Evaluated on one 7B model family via Open LLM Leaderboard and MT-Bench.

