I place TPOUR slightly below TRANSFIR — around **5.4**. The paper has genuine novelty and solid gains, but the combination of benchmark construction bias, missing temporal baselines, ungrounded TRPO formulation, and confounded BEIR analysis constitutes a meaningful cluster of weaknesses that, while not fatal, hold it below the borderline accept threshold.

